SUMMARY:Deadline: RYSE Innovation Hub: Youth Innovation Advisor
DESCRIPTION:RYSE Innovation Hub seeks Youth Innovation Advisors: young peop
 le ages 18 to 24 who are passionate about adolescent health and wellness. 
 Youth Innovation Advisors support projects that strengthen youth engagemen
 t practices and help shape health solutions created with young people in m
 ind. The role is 100% remote\, running from September 2026 to July 2027\, 
 with a time commitment of up to 4 hours per week. WHO IT'S FOR: young peop
 le ages 18 to 24 passionate about adolescent health and wellness. COMPENSA
 TION: USD 480 monthly. DEADLINE: 20 July 2026\, 11:59 PM ET. TO APPLY: sub
 mit the application form.\n\nOrganisation: RYSE Innovation Hub\nLocation: 
 100% remote.\nAward: USD 480 monthly compensation. No application fee.\nDu
 ration: September 2026 to July 2027\; up to 4 hours per week\; 100% remote
 .\n\nMore: http://bit.ly/YIAapp?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_
